<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <title>Feedback Form Landing Page</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0057b8;
            --secondary: #ffd200;
            --accent: #ff5757;
            --bg: #000000;
            --card: #000000;
            --text: #222;
            --muted: #666;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        header {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 40px 0 24px 0;
            border-radius: 0 0 24px 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            padding: 24px 12px;
            margin: 0 auto 32px auto;
            max-width: 420px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .btn {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 10px 28px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            transition: background 0.2s;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding: 20px 10px 16px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--secondary);
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,87,184,0.10);
            border-top: 4px solid var(--accent);
        }
        .feature-card i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: var(--secondary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.97rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        footer {
            background: #fff;
            color: var(--muted);
            padding: 18px 0 10px 0;
            border-radius: 24px 24px 0 0;
            margin-top: 60px;
            box-shadow: 0 -4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .social-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .cta-section {
                padding: 24px 10px;
            }
            .features-grid {
                gap: 18px;
            }
            .feature-card {
                padding: 22px 8px 16px 8px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Feedback Platform</h1>
            <p>Your voice matters! Help us create a better experience by sharing your valuable feedback.</p>
        </div>
    </header>
<br><br>
    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-section">
                <h2>Ready to Share Your Thoughts?</h2>
                <div class="actions">
                    <a href="/register" class="btn"><span>Get Started</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    <h3>Real Impact</h3>
                    <p>Your feedback directly influences our improvements and helps us serve you better.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                    <h3>Easy to Use</h3>
                    <p>Simple and intuitive interface makes providing feedback quick and effortless.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    <h3>Secure & Private</h3>
                    <p>Your responses are confidential and protected with industry-standard security.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            </div>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Feedback Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>